description:
THE RIDE OF YOUR LIFE. Ride 22 motorcycles with the official BMW
Honda, Kawasaki, KTM, Suzuki and Yamaha licences. From 125 to 2000cc
find all of the biggest makes, faithfully reproduced with 3 unique
ways to play: Superbike, Roadster and Custom. Hit the road in
Tournament mode and take on over 40 challenges of skill on 20
different circuits. Customize your riders and challenge rival clubs in
solo mode or in wild online games with up to 4 players

For more infos go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/303830/

